{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Re:Flex is a game where you interact with multiple reactors that appear in time to a song.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">They move smoothly through the mouse, so it feels like you're dancing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Paran: Step in a circle to the beat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Triout: breaking triangles in time with the beat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Han: Avoid explosions that go off in time with the beat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Vizet: dodge targeting missiles with blinks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are multiple designs for each reactor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Paran's cracks design causes shooting stars to explode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Triout's ether design creates three objects that defend against the vizet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy Challenge Mode with a variety of music and logic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is also an editor mode where you can play any song you want with any logic you want.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The First Step","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3221180/ec3181455d5b1f867df29a416bfacda8e32dfa5e.jpg"},{"name":"Open Sandbox","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3221180/3828ffc0d4bc7e5c396d04c0760457fabc181c43.jpg"},{"name":"Open Random Play","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3221180/dfd6091b1ddae0d41516d9053235fa0e948a82ff.jpg"},{"name":"Re:Flexer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3221180/1264d2ac321a12428ee7938f46cad55c0eba552f.jpg"}],"total":4},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3221180?t=1729531089","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221180/page_bg_